  ,                                 !- 23 Heating Cap Ratio Boundary Curve Name
  ,                                 !- 24 Heating Cap Ratio Modifier Function of High Temp Curve Name
  VRF Sys HeatEIRFT,                !- 25 Heating EIR Modifier Function of Low Temp Curve Name
