  0.25,                             !- 33 Minimum Heat Pump Part-Load Ratio
  Event_Hall,                       !- 34 Zone Name for Master Thermostat Location
  MasterThermostatPriority,         !- 35 Master Thermostat Priority Control Type
  ,                                 !- 36 Thermostat Priority Schedule Name
  VRF TU List Event_Hall,           !- 37 Zone Terminal Unit List Name
